你会后悔的
You done stuck your foot in your mouth now.

1643
01:12:04,520 --> 01:12:06,087
朋友, 你要去哪?
Hey, nigger, where you going?

1644
01:12:06,089 --> 01:12:07,522
我得回家
I'm going home.

1645
01:12:07,524 --> 01:12:09,424
你不是在想我会帮你吧
I know you don't expect me to help you now.

1646
01:12:09,426 --> 01:12:10,792
我得保住我的钱
I'm protecting my money.

1647
01:12:11,393 --> 01:12:14,395
我想看你一个人慢慢的建
I want to see you put that fence up by yourself.

1648
01:12:14,397 --> 01:12:15,830
那就是我想看的
That's what I want to see.

1649
01:12:15,832 --> 01:12:18,399
没有我的帮忙, 六个月后你仍然毫无头绪
You'll be here another six months without me.

1650
01:12:18,401 --> 01:12:19,667
朋友, 那样不对啊
Nigger, you ain't right.

1651
01:12:19,669 --> 01:12:21,536
当谈到我的钱
When it come to my money,

1652
01:12:21,538 --> 01:12:24,639
我就像国庆日的烟火一样对[好]
I'm right as fireworks on the Fourth of July.

1653
01:12:24,641 --> 01:12:26,107
等着瞧
We gonna see.

1654
01:12:26,109 --> 01:12:27,809
你准备去提款吧!
You better get out your bank book!

1655
01:13:19,728 --> 01:13:21,863
他们在警局在说了什么? Gabe怎了?
What they say down there? What's happening with Gabe?

1656
01:13:21,865 --> 01:13:24,899
我过去接回他了, 花了我五十块
I went down there and got him out. Cost me $50.

1657
01:13:24,901 --> 01:13:26,601
说他在扰乱秩序
Said he was disturbing the peace.

1658
01:13:26,603 --> 01:13:28,903
法官三周后审讯
Judge set up a hearing for him in three weeks

1659
01:13:28,905 --> 01:13:31,706
他为何不被重新分配到医院内
to show cause why he shouldn't be recommitted.

1660
01:13:31,708 --> 01:13:33,574
那你怎说? 你怎跟法官说的
What'd you say? What'd you tell the judge?

1661
01:13:33,742 --> 01:13:35,610
我跟他说我会照顾他
I told him I'd take care of him.

1662
01:13:35,612 --> 01:13:37,178
没有理由又分配他住医院
It didn't make no sense to recommit the man.

1663
01:13:37,180 --> 01:13:38,679
他伸出他那贪婪的手
He stuck out his big greasy palm,

1664
01:13:38,681 --> 01:13:41,482
跟我说交出$50然后带他回家
told me to give him $50 and take him on home.

1665
01:13:41,484 --> 01:13:43,484
那他现在在哪?
Where's he at now? Where'd he go off to?

1666
01:13:43,486 --> 01:13:45,486
又到处乱跑了, 他不想别人拖着他的手
Gone about his business. He don't need nobody to hold his hand.

1667
01:13:45,488 --> 01:13:47,722
我也不知道, 但那看来是最好的选择
Well, I don't know, seem like that would be the best place for him.

1668
01:13:47,724 --> 01:13:48,756
让他住在医院里
To put him in a hospital.

1669
01:13:48,758 --> 01:13:49,891
我知道你接下来要说什么
I know what you say gonna say,

1670
01:13:49,893 --> 01:13:51,526
但那正是我认为这样做是对的原因
but that's what I think would be best.

1671
01:13:51,528 --> 01:13:53,161
那他在打仗时失去的一切, 为了什么?
Man had his life ruined fighting for what?

1672
01:13:53,163 --> 01:13:54,595
现在他们想把他锁起来?
Now, they want to take him and lock him up?

1673
01:13:54,597 --> 01:13:56,898
该给他自由啊, 他又没打扰谁
Let him be free. Man ain't bothering nobody.

1674
01:13:56,900 --> 01:14:00,768
我想每个人都有不同的看法
Everybody got their own way of looking at it, I guess.

1675
01:14:00,770 --> 01:14:02,170
来拿你的午餐吧
Come on, get your lunch.

1676
01:14:02,172 --> 01:14:03,805
我这里有些棉豆和玉米面包
I got some lima beans and cornbread in the oven.

1677
01:14:03,877 --> 01:14:04,977
快去, 你得吃点什么
Come on, get somethin' to eat.

1678
01:14:05,007 --> 01:14:06,741
在这里烦恼Gabe的事也没帮助
Ain't no sense in you fretting over Gabe.

1679
01:14:06,813 --> 01:14:07,913
Rose, 我有点事要跟你说
Rose, I got something to tell you.

1680
01:14:07,943 --> 01:14:10,912
- 待我把食物放好再说   - Rose...
- Wait till I put the food on the table. - Rose...

1681
01:14:11,747 --> 01:14:14,715
我不知道该怎开口
Now, I don't know how to tell you this.

1682
01:14:18,554 --> 01:14:20,655
但又不能瞒着你
And I can't explain it none.

1683
01:14:20,657 --> 01:14:23,825
[好感]就那么一点点的积聚啊
It just sort of grows on you.

1684
01:14:24,760 --> 01:14:27,895
开始时就像小木灌
It started off like a little bush,

1685
01:14:27,897 --> 01:14:29,530
待你发现时已经是整片森林了
next thing you know, it's a whole forest.

1686
01:14:29,532 --> 01:14:30,765
Troy, 你在说什么?
Troy, what is you talking about?

1687
01:14:30,767 --> 01:14:32,667
我在说话, 女人, 让我把话说完
I'm talking, woman. Let me talk.

1688
01:14:32,669 --> 01:14:34,635
我在跟你说
I'm trying to tell you,

1689
01:14:34,637 --> 01:14:36,938
我在找个隐晦的方法跟你说...
find a way to tell you that...

1690
01:14:41,944 --> 01:14:44,579
我要成为父亲了
I'm gonna be a daddy.

1691
01:14:46,648 --> 01:14:48,850
对, 我要成为别人的父亲了
Yeah, I'm gonna be somebody's daddy.

1692
01:14:53,555 --> 01:14:56,224
Troy, 不是真的吧? 你要成为什么?
Troy, you ain't telling me this. You're gonna be what?

1693
01:14:56,226 --> 01:14:57,692
- 你要成为别人的父亲?   - Rose...
- You're gonna be somebody's daddy?   - Rose...

1694
01:14:57,694 --> 01:14:58,793
你竟然跟你的妻子说这个?
You're telling your wife this?

1695
01:14:58,795 --> 01:14:59,861
现在...
Now...

1696
01:14:59,863 --> 01:15:02,230
嗨, Troy, 嗨, Rose
Hey, Troy! Hey, Rose!

1697
01:15:02,232 --> 01:15:04,866
我等了18年就为了听你说这些事吗?
I got to wait 18 years to hear something like this?

1698
01:15:04,868 --> 01:15:06,501
嗨, Rose
Hey, Rose.

1699
01:15:07,971 --> 01:15:10,638
我有朵花送给你
I got a flower for you.

1700
01:15:12,975 --> 01:15:16,777
那是朵玫瑰花, 就像你的名字一样
That's a rose. The same rose like you is.

1701
01:15:21,717 --> 01:15:23,017
谢了, Gabe
Thanks, Gabe.

1702
01:15:23,019 --> 01:15:24,689
Troy, 你没在生我的气吧?
Troy, you ain't mad at me?

1703
01:15:24,691 --> 01:15:26,719
那些坏人抓了我回来
Them bad mens come and put me away.

1704
01:15:26,721 --> 01:15:28,723
- 你没在生我的气吧?   - 没, 我没有生气
- You ain't mad at me?   - No. No, I ain't mad at you.

1705
01:15:28,725 --> 01:15:30,725
18年了, 你竟然做得出这种事?
Eighteen years, and you want to come with this?

1706
01:15:30,727 --> 01:15:33,561
看我拿到了什么? 一个全新的25美分
See what I got? Got a brand-new quarter.

1707
01:15:36,264 --> 01:15:37,465
Rose, 只是...
Rose, it's just that...

1708
01:15:37,966 --> 01:15:39,734
你没什么可以说, 也不用解释
Ain't nothing you can say, Troy. Ain't no explaining it.

1709
01:15:39,736 --> 01:15:42,603
给我这25美分的人还有一大堆
The fella that give me this quarter had a whole mess of 'em!

1710
01:15:42,605 --> 01:15:44,939
我要留着它直到它暗哑无光
I'm gonna keep this quarter till it stops shining.

1711
01:15:44,941 --> 01:15:47,742
Gabe, 出去前门等我, 我冰箱里有西瓜
Gabe, go on up front now.
I got some watermelon in the frigidaire.

1712
01:15:47,814 --> 01:15:48,914
快去, 我待会拿给你
Go on. I'll get you a piece.

1713
01:15:48,944 --> 01:15:51,746
Rose, 听我说, 我当时在追赶地狱之犬
Say, Rose, you know, I was chasing hellhounds,

1714
01:15:51,748 --> 01:15:54,749
然后那些坏人把我抓回去锁起来了
and them bad mens come and get me and take me away.

1715
01:15:54,751 --> 01:15:56,817
Troy救了我, 他来了并跟他们说
Troy helped me. He come down there and told them

1716
01:15:56,819 --> 01:15:59,820
他们最好在他打跨他们之前放了我
they better let me go before he beat them up!

1717
01:15:59,892 --> 01:16:00,992
他真的说了
Yeah, he did!

1718
01:16:01,022 --> 01:16:03,624
出去吧, Gabe, 我待会给你西瓜
Go up front now, Gabe. I'll get you some watermelon.

1719
01:16:03,626 --> 01:16:04,959
那些坏人都走了
Them bad men is gone now.

1720
01:16:04,961 --> 01:16:07,628
好吧, Rose要给我西瓜
Okay. Rose gonna give me some watermelon,

1721
01:16:07,630 --> 01:16:09,997
有条纹的那种
the kind with the stripes on it.

1722
01:16:15,637 --> 01:16:16,938
为什么, Troy?
Why, Troy?

1723
01:16:18,739 --> 01:16:19,740
为什么?
Why?

1724
01:16:19,741 --> 01:16:25,646
过了那么多年, 你现在跟我说这些?
After all these years, you come dragging this in to me now?

1725
01:16:25,648 --> 01:16:27,815
你这年纪, 不应该会做的
It don't make no sense at your age.

1726
01:16:28,317 --> 01:16:32,353
我可以理解你十年或者十五年前这样做, 但不是现在
I could've expected this 10, or 15 years ago, but not now.

1727
01:16:32,355 --> 01:16:34,822
年龄与此没有关系, Rose
Age ain't got nothing to do with it, Rose.

1728
01:16:38,794 --> 01:16:42,029
我做了一个妻子该做的
I done tried to be everything a wife should be.

1729
01:16:43,966 --> 01:16:45,637
一个妻子可以做的所有事
Everything a wife could be.

1730
01:16:45,667 --> 01:16:46,838
我结婚整整18年了
I've been married 18 years,

1731
01:16:47,168 --> 01:16:49,337
而现在竟到了你说
and now, I got to live to see the day you tell me

1732
01:16:49,339 --> 01:16:52,940
你和别的女人有了孩子的一天
you been seeing another woman and done fathered a child by her.

1733
01:17:05,988 --> 01:17:10,057
你明知道我不喜欢同父异母什么的
And you know I never wanted no half-nothing in my family!

1734
01:17:12,995 --> 01:17:14,362
我整个家庭都是这样
My whole family is half.

1735
01:17:14,364 --> 01:17:16,130
每个人都有不同的父母亲
Everybody got different fathers and mothers

1736
01:17:16,132 --> 01:17:17,898
我的几个兄弟姊妹都是这样
and my two sisters and my brothers.

1737
01:17:17,900 --> 01:17:19,700
你根本不知道谁是谁生的
You could hardly tell who's who.

1738
01:17:19,702 --> 01:17:21,369
永远不能好好谈谈父母的话题
Could never sit down and talk about papa and mama.

1739
01:17:21,371 --> 01:17:24,038
因为大家的父母都不一样
It was always your papa, your mama, my papa, my mama.

1740
01:17:24,040 --> 01:17:26,807
我从不想我的孩子们也是这样
And I ain't never wanted that for none of my children!

1741
01:17:26,809 --> 01:17:28,042
然而现在, 你竟然过来
And now, you want to drag your behind in here

1742
01:17:28,114 --> 01:17:29,214
跟我说这些事!
and tell me something like this!

1743
01:17:29,244 --> 01:17:32,178
够了, 你有权利知道的, 是时候了
Stop it now. You ought to know. It's time for you to know.

1744
01:17:32,180 --> 01:17:33,080
我才不想知道, 妈的!
Well, I don't want to know, god damn it!

1745
01:17:53,000 --> 01:17:54,001
Rose?
Rose?

1746
01:17:57,139 --> 01:18:00,808
我不能让她堕胎, 米已成炊了
I just can't make it go away. It's done now.

1747
01:18:00,810 --> 01:18:04,879
我没法改变事情
I can't wish the circumstances of the thing away.

1748
01:18:04,881 --> 01:18:07,448
你也不想改变
And you don't want to, either.

1749
01:18:07,450 --> 01:18:09,216
或许你想我们两母子离开
Maybe you want to wish me and my boy away.

1750
01:18:09,218 --> 01:18:10,885
也许那就是你想的
Maybe that's what you want.

1751
01:18:10,887 --> 01:18:13,421
你不能这样做
Well, you can't wish us away.

1752
01:18:13,423 --> 01:18:15,456
我把我的18年放在你身上了
I got 18 years of my life invested in you.

1753
01:18:15,458 --> 01:18:17,725
你该留在我们的床上而不是出去鬼混
You ought to have stayed upstairs in my bed where you belong.

1754
01:18:17,727 --> 01:18:20,161
听着, 我们可以处理好这事
Now, listen to me. We can get a handle on this thing.

1755
01:18:20,163 --> 01:18:22,296
我们可以说清楚, 有共识
We can talk this out, come to an understanding.

1756
01:18:22,298 --> 01:18:23,464
突然间此事就是关于"我们"
All of a sudden it's "we."

1757
01:18:23,466 --> 01:18:24,899
当你在外面
Where was "we" at when
you were down there,

1758
01:18:24,901 --> 01:18:26,467
跟那个可恶的女人鬼混时"我们"在哪里?
rolling around with some godforsaken woman?

1759
01:18:26,469 --> 01:18:27,702
"我们"该在你做傻事之前
"We" should've come to an understanding

1760
01:18:27,704 --> 01:18:29,136
就要有共识!
before you started making a damn fool of yourself!

1761
01:18:29,138 --> 01:18:30,805
当说到共识时
You're a day late and a dollar short

1762
01:18:30,807 --> 01:18:32,106
你总是迟了
when it comes to an understanding with me.

1763
01:18:32,108 --> 01:18:38,012
Rose, 只是因为她能给我完全不同的感觉
Rose, it's just that she...gives me a different idea.

1764
01:18:38,447 --> 01:18:41,782
完全不同的自我理解
A different understanding about myself.

1765
01:18:41,784 --> 01:18:45,152
让我可以在这里走出去时, 放下所有压力
I can step out of this house and get away from the pressures

1766
01:18:45,154 --> 01:18:46,787
和问题, 变成一个完全不同的人
and the problems, be a different man.

1767
01:18:46,789 --> 01:18:48,723
我不用担心如何修好屋顶
I ain't got to worry about how I'll get the roof fixed,

1768
01:18:48,725 --> 01:18:50,191
或者付钱, 或者...
or pay the bills, or...

1769
01:18:50,193 --> 01:18:51,826
我可以
I can just

1770
01:18:53,729 --> 01:18:56,163
成为一个我前所未有过的自己
be a part of myself I ain't never been before.

1771
01:18:57,232 --> 01:18:59,767
我想知道的是...
What I want to know is...

1772
01:19:02,037 --> 01:19:04,772
我想知道的是
What I want to know

1773
01:19:04,774 --> 01:19:07,241
你是否打算继续见她?
is do you plan to continue seeing her?

1774
01:19:07,243 --> 01:19:09,877
那就是你可以说的
That's all you can say to me.

1775
01:19:10,979 --> 01:19:12,813
我在她的家里能放松下来
I could sit up in her house and laugh.

1776
01:19:12,815 --> 01:19:15,082
你明白吗?
You understand what I'm saying?

1777
01:19:15,084 --> 01:19:17,885
我可以放声笑, 而那感觉真好
I could laugh out loud, and it feels good.

1778
01:19:17,887 --> 01:19:20,087
简直好到了我心底里
It reaches all the way down to the bottom of my shoes.

1779
01:19:20,089 --> 01:19:21,288
Rose, 我...
Rose, I...

1780
01:19:23,825 --> 01:19:26,794
我不想放弃那些
I can't give that up.

1781
01:19:32,234 --> 01:19:34,535
那或许你该继续留在她那里
Well, maybe you ought to go on and stay down there with her,

1782
01:19:34,537 --> 01:19:36,237
如果她真是比我更好的女人的话
if she's a better woman than me.

1783
01:19:36,239 --> 01:19:38,105
这不是关于谁是更好的女人的问题
It ain't about nobody being a better woman, or nothing.

1784
01:19:38,177 --> 01:19:39,177
Rose, 你尽责了
Rose, you ain't to blame.

1785
01:19:39,207 --> 01:19:41,976
做妻子的话你简直是不二之选
A man couldn't ask for a better wife than you've been.

1786
01:19:41,978 --> 01:19:43,481
这事我得负起所有责任
I'm responsible for it.

1787
01:19:43,483 --> 01:19:45,511
我每天重复做着同样的事
I done locked myself into a pattern,

1788
01:19:45,513 --> 01:19:47,181
照顾你们, 都让我忘了自己了
trying to take care of you all, that I forgot about myself.

1789
01:19:47,183 --> 01:19:48,983
我不是一直在你背后吗?
Well, what the hell was I there for?

1790
01:19:48,985 --> 01:19:50,551
那是我的工作, 不是他人的
That was my job, not somebody else's.

1791
01:19:50,553 --> 01:19:53,854
Rose, 听着, 我竭尽所能去过正当的生活
Rose, listen to me. I done tried all my life to live decent.

1792
01:19:53,856 --> 01:19:56,857
一个正当, 努力向上的生活
To live a clean, hard, useful life.

1793
01:19:56,859 --> 01:20:00,027
我尽了力去成为一个好丈夫
I try to be a good husband to you, in every way I know how.

1794
01:20:00,029 --> 01:20:02,196
可能我一开始就错了吧, 我不知道
Maybe I come into the world backwards, I don't know,

1795
01:20:02,198 --> 01:20:05,833
但你就像上场前已经被二振了一样
but you're born with two strikes on you before you come to the plate.

1796
01:20:05,905 --> 01:20:06,905
你得把任何事都看管好
You got to guard it closely,

1797
01:20:06,935 --> 01:20:09,570
老是担心突发事情
always looking for the curveball on the inside corner.

1798
01:20:09,572 --> 01:20:11,238
你不能让任何事不受你控制
You can't afford a called strike.

1799
01:20:11,240 --> 01:20:12,873
你不能让任何事漏掉
You can't let nothing get past you.

1800
01:20:12,875 --> 01:20:15,009
要是你倒下了, 你还不死心
If you're going down, you're doing down swinging.

1801
01:20:15,011 --> 01:20:17,912
所有事都像对着你干一样
Everything lined up against you!

1802
01:20:19,281 --> 01:20:21,015
你还想怎样?
What you gonna do?

1803
01:20:22,350 --> 01:20:25,052
我赢了他们, Rose, 我短打了 [牺牲]
I fooled them, Rose. I bunted.

1804
01:20:25,287 --> 01:20:29,223
当我有你和Cory和份有点像样的工作, 我很安全
When I found you and Cory and a halfway decent job, I was safe.

1805
01:20:29,225 --> 01:20:31,559
没什么可以拖累我了
Couldn't nothing touch me!

1806
01:20:31,561 --> 01:20:33,127
我不会再被三振出局
I wasn't gonna strike out no more.

1807
01:20:33,129 --> 01:20:34,562
不会再回去坐牢
I wasn't going back to the penitentiary.

1808
01:20:34,564 --> 01:20:37,031
不会再喝醉, 睡在街上
I wasn't gonna lie in the street with a bottle of wine.

1809
01:20:37,033 --> 01:20:41,302
我安全了, 我有个家庭, 有份工作
I was safe. I had me a family, a job.

1810
01:20:42,337 --> 01:20:45,206
我不会被三振的
I wasn't gonna get that last strike.

1811
01:20:47,042 --> 01:20:49,977
我站在一垒
I was standing on first base,

1812
01:20:49,979 --> 01:20:53,012
等着回到本垒
waiting for one of them boys to
knock me in, to bring me home.

1813
01:20:53,014 --> 01:20:53,884
你该留在我们的床上, Troy
You should have stayed in my bed, Troy.

1814
01:20:53,886 --> 01:20:55,914
然后我看到那女子, 她让我胆大起来
Then I saw the gal, she firmed up my backbone.

1815
01:20:55,916 --> 01:20:58,285
我在想如果我努力点, 或许可以盗垒
I got to thinkin' that if I tried, maybe I could steal second.

1816
01:20:58,287 --> 01:21:00,087
- 你明白吗?   - 你该抱紧我
- You understand what I'm saying? - You should've held me tight.

1817
01:21:00,089 --> 01:21:02,388
你该捉紧我的手
You should've grabbed me and held on.

1818
01:21:02,390 --> 01:21:03,324
我站在一垒18年了
I stood on first base for 18 years,

1819
01:21:03,326 --> 01:21:05,960
