and I buried them inside you.

1844
01:22:03,653 --> 01:22:06,086
我把种子埋藏好, 每天看着它, 祈望它成长
I planted a seed and watched and prayed over it.

1845
01:22:06,088 --> 01:22:09,123
我把自己埋藏在你心内然后等待开花!
I planted myself inside you and waited to bloom!

1846
01:22:09,125 --> 01:22:10,991
但那花了我18年时间
And it didn't take me no 18 years

1847
01:22:10,993 --> 01:22:13,093
才知道那泥土原来如石头般硬
to realize the soil was hard and rocky,

1848
01:22:13,095 --> 01:22:15,195
