hang out at Taylors' with the boys.

1892
01:27:31,083 --> 01:27:32,283
或许玩一局[西洋]跳棋
Maybe play a game of checkers.

1893
01:27:32,313 --> 01:27:34,781
Troy, 我不能再继续这样, 我接受不了
Troy, I can't live like this. I won't live like this.

1894
01:27:34,783 --> 01:27:36,450
自那之后你就人在心不在
You're living on borrowed time with me.

1895
01:27:36,452 --> 01:27:38,485
六个月以来, 你都没真正回来
Been going on six months now, you ain't been coming home.

1896
01:27:38,487 --> 01:27:40,587
我每晚都回来, 一年来从没间断过
I come home every night. Every night of the year.

1897
01:27:40,589 --> 01:27:43,323
那就整整365天
That's 365 days.

1898
01:27:44,592 --> 01:27:47,394
我想你明天下班后直接回家
I want you to come home tomorrow after work.

1899
01:27:52,333 --> 01:27:55,802
Rose, 你知道我不会乱花钱
Rose, I don't mess up my pay. You know that.

1900
01:27:55,804 --> 01:27:57,771
我收到工资后就全数交给你
I take my pay, i give it to you.

1901
01:27:57,773 --> 01:28:01,441
我只拿着你分配给我的部份
I don't have no money but what you give me back.

1902
01:28:01,443 --> 01:28:04,611
我只想要一点私人时间而已
I just want a little time to myself.

1903
01:28:04,613 --> 01:28:05,779
去享乐一下
A little time to enjoy life.

1904
01:28:05,781 --> 01:28:07,748
那我呢? 何时才轮到我去享乐?
What about me? When's my time to enjoy life?

1905
01:28:07,750 --> 01:28:10,017
我不知道还可以说什么, 我已经尽力了
I don't know what to tell you, Rose. I'm doing the best I can.

1906
01:28:10,089 --> 01:28:11,381
你下班回家后
You ain't been comin' home from work,

1907
01:28:11,411 --> 01:28:12,587
只换件衣服又出去了
but time enough to change your clothes and run out.

1908
